"Sounds good, I'll toggle the blue locked door and meet you at the box. I'll drop the blue key there too."
"I'll move forward to the box now, and then I'll pick it up. Please hurry up with the door so we can complete the mission."
"Got it, I'll forward to the door and toggle it, then I'll forward again to meet you at the box. Let's do this!"
"I've reached the box, I'll pick it up now. Meet you there, let's complete the mission!"
